Task: Write a query to find the top 5 customers in the top 10 cities who have paid the highest total amounts to Rockbuster.
Explanation: A SQL syntax using an inner join which shows all films by genre, rating, language, number of rentals, and total profit made. 

SELECT 
  A.customer_id, 
  A.first_name AS "customer first name",
  A.last_name AS "customer last name",
  D.country,
  C.city,
  SUM(E.amount) AS "total amount paid"
FROM customer A
INNER JOIN address B ON A.address_id = B.address_id
INNER JOIN city C on B.city_id = C.city_id
INNER JOIN country D on C.country_id = D.country_id
INNER JOIN payment E ON A.customer_id = E.customer_id
WHERE city IN('Aurora','Acua','Citrus Heights','Iwaki','Ambattur','Shanwei','So Leopoldo','Teboksary','Tianjin','Cianjur')
GROUP BY A.customer_id,
  first_name, 
  last_name, 
  country,
  city
ORDER BY "total amount paid" DESC
LIMIT 5
